The provider name should be updated as long as the institution name, city, state and country in the spreadsheet match the information listed in SIDB2

Institution name can match either the primary Institution Name or an Alias listed in SIDB2

Both scenarios should be considered a valid match

If multiple database listings match on name and location, all matching listings should be updated


For records where the system is unable to find a match and update automatically, a list of those records should be shared back with Ops for review and possible manual updates
